name: What is Art?
description: A multi-layered digital artwork made in collaboration with Kim. Using an abstract photograph from Kim's iconic works, and a WIP edit from my previous HAYSTICKS mint. Patterns of life take form and shape, few discernible, few discern our selves from within. For example, colours are discernible in art, the abstractions of a frame, discern itself. I wonder what this depends on.  || @jubujubumeerumeeru x @ayushbanerjee
